        "title": "The QCD running coupling at all scales and the connection between hadron masses and Lambda_s",
        "description": "We report on recent experimental and theoretical developments in our understanding of the QCD running coupling $\\alpha_s$ in QCD's nonperturbative regime. They allow us to analytically compute the hadron mass spectrum, with $\\Lambda_s$ the only input necessary to this determination. The computed spectra agrees well with experimental data.",
